{"tid":2404044,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"利嘉閣：買家情緒樂觀向好 逾千組客周末約睇樓","createTime":"2021-02-11T12:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T01:56:36.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60ef152070c6548744f7bad5926494b9fc4d5ad5","tid":2404044,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:54:06.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣：買家情緒樂觀向好 逾千組客周末約睇樓<br />\n20:15 2021/02/11<br />\n<br />\n&quot;利嘉閣地產研究部主管陳海潮表示，雖然今年農曆新年市民減少外遊，惟部分買家、業主難免要出門拜年過節，導致新春長假期二手屋苑預約睇樓量受壓。根據利嘉閣地產研究部數據估算，全港50個指標屋苑共錄1,080組客戶於周末預約睇樓，按周下挫28.0%，終止6連升，而四天長假則約有1,240組客戶。今年港股升勢強勁，市場憧憬中美兩國關係改善，買家情緒樂觀向好，加上多個新盤醞釀推出，相信新春長假期過後，市況將出現較大反彈動力.......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2877492/%E5%88%A9%E5%98%89%E9%96%A3%EF%BC%9A%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E5%90%91%E5%A5%BD%20%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E7%B5%84%E5%AE%A2%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E7%B4%84%E7%9D%87%E6%A8%93?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2877492%2F%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2596%25A3%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A5%25BD%2520%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%259C%25AB%25E7%25B4%2584%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%25A8%2593%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=43266e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2877492/%E5%88%A9%E5%98%89%E9%96%A3%EF%BC%9A%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80%E5%90%91%E5%A5%BD%20%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E7%B5%84%E5%AE%A2%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E7%B4%84%E7%9D%87%E6%A8%93?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"3e9c18748158a233c8234983857d01783f8a6964","tid":2404044,"uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"廢淡情緒也高漲"},{"pid":"52fe2490e1aa0a380540e107990e2a6cbb74aa78","tid":2404044,"uid":244215,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime